span.span: The MISSION of the SWSD is to:
Offer all students the opportunity to achieve an excellent education;
Prepare students to be life-long learners through cooperation of staff, parents and community;
Graduate academically and socially well-rounded students to be productive members of society;
Consider the long-range financial effect on the community.
The fitness center is closed until further notice.

div.p: It is with great pleasure to share with you our district and buildingreport cards. Our district has made significant gains in these reports.
High School --Improved from 66.4 (Meets Expectations) to 80.3 (Exceeds expectations).
Elementary--Improved from 80.3(Meets Expectations to 83.6 (Significantly Exceeds Expectations).

A job well done by all our staff, school board and administration. Please feel free to call the district office if you have questions about these report cards. Everyday is a great day to be a Wildcat!
